    </div>
    <div>
        <h3><b>Subject: <u>1st Reminder Notice on Overdue Installments</u></b></h3>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <p>That subject file is provisionally book in your name and management of The Grand City is regretfully pointed out that an amount of Rs. <b>@string.Format("{0:n0}", Math.Round(Convert.ToDecimal(Model.Select(x => x.Balance_Amount))))/-</b> is outstanding against you, as arrears of Installments regarding your file.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
