                <p>Details of account is as under:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Account No. 0000-102535994087 &nbsp;&nbsp; Bank Al Baraka</li>
                    <li>Account No. 0023-487000510503 &nbsp;&nbsp; Bank HBL</li>
                    <li>Account No. 0109-000228187019 &nbsp;&nbsp; Bank UBL</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Please treat this letter as <b>1st REMINDER NOTICE</b>, failing which the management of The Grand City will be constrained to take an appropriate action as per rules & policies, which includes the cancellation of provisional allotment / sale agreement of your file.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><b><u>In case you have already paid installment / dues of your file, please disregard this notice.</u></b></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Assuring you of full cooperation and you may visit our site office or head office at any working hours for further assistance.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="signature-line"></div>
        <p>Company Official Signature</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

